Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.35,0:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,First chapter name...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Complete!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.78,0:00:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way better than before!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, even I can tell!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.99,0:00:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin, let Hattori know.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.07,0:00:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.04,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,In only five days,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.04,0:00:27.59,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,they've redone it from \Nscratch and taken it this far!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.25,0:00:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much better!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you two \Ndidn't get much sleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.05,0:00:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.51,0:00:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,how else can we fix it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it get better?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.01,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that it can definitely beat Niizuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.48,0:00:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the title okay as is?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a bit stiff.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.65,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be more \Nshounen manga-like.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.90,0:00:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's the tried-and-true method of putting the protagonist's name in the title.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.45,0:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like {\i1}Captain Tsubasa{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.12,0:01:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.16,0:01:02.66,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tanto{\i0} was like that too.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.66,0:01:06.54,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,That way you know right away what it's about and who's the main character.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.54,0:01:08.97,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,It's certainly easy to tell from that,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.97,0:01:10.75,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,and it's simple and easy to remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.01,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.01,0:01:14.92,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,"Chimitsu Kei" doesn't leave much of an impression.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.84,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,It may be too plain for a main character.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oozora Tsubasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.51,0:01:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakuragi Hanamichi.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.97,0:01:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a well-defined name with as much impact as those.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A name suitable for \Na main character...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.73,0:01:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of main characters,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.27,0:01:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,there's one more \Nthing you need to fix.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.65,0:01:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A design suitable for\N a main character.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the setting calls for a \Nnormal elementary school kid,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.04,0:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we want it to be realistic,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so to a certain degree it's okay,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's just too normal right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no difference between\N him and his classmates.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The impact of his appearance...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more important\N than his name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.42,0:01:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs to have a \Nspecial characteristic.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do his character design.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi, you worry about \Nthe name and the title.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's redo all the main \Ncharacters' names, not just his.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.64,0:01:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.39,0:02:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think of them as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.45,0:02:04.68,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hurry with the names, since we can just cut and paste them in.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.68,0:02:07.73,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,But the character design needs to come first, so I have to hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.93,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I've given them all the advice I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.68,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you two assistants.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made sure they're\N suited to your art style.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.40,0:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and we've got \NOrihara on board too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting backwards...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.58,0:02:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make it if we start the\N manuscript around the 13th.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.61,0:02:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The 13th is the New Year's party.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.74,0:02:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If we have a new serialization,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to go, don't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.41,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,The New Year's party.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.58,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I want to do what \Nmy uncle couldn't do,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.34,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,and the things he left undone.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.42,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What he couldn't do?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.97,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What he left undone?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.64,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What he couldn't do
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.64,0:02:41.51,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,was make a living\N off of manga alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.15,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What he left undone
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.89,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,was getting first \Nplace in the survey!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the coming of age \Nceremony over already?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I let you keep \Nworking alone when I haven't 
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,come up with character\N names or a title yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwase and Ishizawa were there too,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.01,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so we ducked out early.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've really drawn a lot of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a hundred.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've drawn everything I could think of.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there one that jumps out at you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.79,0:04:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who knows\N the most about art.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good with whatever\N you come up with.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't come up with anything yet, which is why I'm still drawing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we want to keep things realistic,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a limit to what \NI can do with the hair.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want an elementary \Nschool kid looking like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.81,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't go to today's \NNew Year's party, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Abe!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw each other at the ceremony.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not home yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi isn't coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're working hard, aren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they'd give up this brief time of enjoyment.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that outfit, Akira?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's punishment for the editors whose authors didn't show up.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Yuujirou?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda is still \Ndrawing his manuscript.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Fukuda isn't here either?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these people thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.60,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiramaru.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.77,0:05:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to work harder too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the hardworking folks work hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, I can take a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm living large with these Otter figures selling like pancakes!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want one too?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.62,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An Otter figure—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.12,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiramaru-sensei, I misjudged you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You are conceited.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just joking!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You got what you \Ndeserved, Hiramaru.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.47,0:06:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your latest manuscript was fantastic.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you for the rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become the\N best in the business.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm expecting art that's even better than your usual quality.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.74,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,The editor swap put\N a fire under Akina.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.74,0:06:29.03,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,We've got some powerful \Nrivals, Ashirogi Muto!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuujirou.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you're up.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we seriously doing this?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the moment \Nyou've all been waiting for!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.71,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is the Hattori combo,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.60,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Giraffe Akira and Zebra \NYuujirou with {\i1}Otters 11{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.30,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we couldn't make\N it to the New Year's party.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.22,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it, this is \Npart of an editor's job.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, I've finished \Nthe character design!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going back to the office.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.50,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you send me a fax?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.90,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone strap idea is good.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he changes modes\N with glasses isn't forced.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.74,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.79,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this in the manuscript right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to be working with you again!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we made you wait for half a year.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.01,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown over this past year,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.31,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm ready to \Nbust my tail for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The new assistants will be \Nhere soon, won't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Moriya and Shiratori, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He said they're both \Nyounger than us, I think.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time our \Nassistants will all be younger.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting kind of nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're shy, Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, about this Moriya guy...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was a finalist for the \Nmost recent Tezuka prize.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some strange art.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's good.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He has design sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find anything on Shiratori.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Moriya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one year \Nyounger than you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He was attending design school,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but after he was a finalist\N for the Tezuka prize,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.60,0:08:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,he left to draw manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm aiming to be a mangaka,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it would be quicker\N if I start out as an assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Shiratori.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.46,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He just graduated from\N high school last year.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.60,0:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He applied to be an\N assistant for Niizuma,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but his assistants had \Nalready been decided on,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so I brought him over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get in to art school and was wondering what I was going to do...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,when I saw the \Nrecruitment for assistants.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love drawing, so I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't actually drawn \Nany manga before, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I like reading them.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.87,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee their skill.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to \Nworking with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to \Nworking with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.76,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your third serialization.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take it from here, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give you \Neach a copy of two pages
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.60,0:09:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of the manuscript with a rough sketch of the backgrounds.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please draw it in.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll choose one of you to do backgrounds
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.47,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the style doesn't \Nchange from page to page.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So only one of us\N will be able to draw?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.68,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Skill is a given,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.80,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,but they need speed\N and sense too...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.80,0:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.80,0:09:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look over it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll only decide once\N Orihara is finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I'm getting nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiratori to do backgrounds.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, I get to draw!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, Shiratori!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.20,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why him?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His art is nearest to\N what I imagined.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the style of this \Nmanga is solidified,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have Shiratori do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.68,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this {\i1}Perfect \NCrime Club{\i0} is really good!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I like how it's unique.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.90,0:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The title's still a placeholder. I'm planning on changing it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The main character's name too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have the time,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.72,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep nitpicking over the details until I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think the title
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.28,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and the main character's name will really affect the rankings.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really thinking this through.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rankings, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong \Nabout stuff like rankings.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in drawing\N manga just to get popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.51,0:11:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But manga is for \Neveryone to enjoy, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Popularity is important.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't draw a good \Nmanga if you think like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.89,0:11:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q0}Though since you don't draw any manga,\N I suppose it has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's {\i1}your{\i0} ideal manga?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.82,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, manga is a form of \Nself-expression and a fine art.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.61,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe all manga should be thus.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine art, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it that way, you'll feel good about yourself, but it won't sell.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack is a business,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so the manga has to appeal\N to a majority of people.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious that rankings
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.18,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and sales figures are important?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.34,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To try and draw for Jack \Nwithout understanding that...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiratori, you've gone too far!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}your{\i0} opinion.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.56,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We are trying to get this to sell.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's because we\N don't have the talent.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Parents used to say to their kids...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.71,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,well, maybe they're still saying this...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Reading manga makes you stupid."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.16,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't let them read it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.12,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But manga gradually came to be recognized as having cultural value.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I think you should draw a manga with content
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.72,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and quality that you wouldn't be ashamed to say has cultural value.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.09,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But since we don't have\N the ability to do that,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.81,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to draw it \Nwith popularity in mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's okay for anyone\N to draw manga like that,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.81,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in accordance with their abilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, everyone should \Ndraw in their own way.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.50,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.92,0:12:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what was going to happen during that argument!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like they're at opposite ends of the spectrum.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say \Nwho's right or wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Opposites, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Opposite?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I could turn this around...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too caught up with \Nthe idea of a perfect crime.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If I think along the lines of them not committing real crimes, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.11,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.53,0:13:28.28,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,If you put them together, that's "morals" and "truth."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.64,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,They fit the main characters,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.64,0:13:31.04,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,since they're the opposite of "crime."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Doumoto Makoto.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga Minoru.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And Annojo Mai!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're kinda cool, even!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're great.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.04,0:13:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with that!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awesome, Akito!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what happens when\N I get a flash of intuition.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.48,0:13:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about the title?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got that yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's disappointing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}Well, we still have a few days \Nbefore we need to finish.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a perfect manuscript!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The story and art are a given,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but the protagonist's \Nnames are good too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And this title—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.24,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Crime
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Party.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.17,0:14:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Japanese translation is "Perfect Crime Party."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching the news
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought "party" as in "political party" would work well.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Party" has a cheerful image,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.86,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and since it's also used in video games, I thought it would make it seem fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A typical Takagi analysis.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The effort you two put\N into this really shows.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.08,0:14:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely get first \Nplace for the first chapter!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've put everything we possibly could into this to accomplish that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think aiming for that with this manuscript is more than reasonable.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.11,0:14:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest depends on Fukuda's one-shot, since that'll be in the issue too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda's one-shot?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear about this!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.62,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I said it was impossible to do a one-shot and {\i1}Kiyoshi{\i0} at the same time!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.62,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave me your permission!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm helping you right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But this manga is good!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Road Racer Buchigiri{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a super car boom.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll cause a super bike boom!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bad to have a hobby.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because you\N said that to me, Yuujirou.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to you for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.81,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm pissed that it's in the same issue as Ashirogi's first chapter!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.27,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It means they want to compare it with a new serialization.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.24,0:15:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The editorial department \Nput some thought into it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Ashirogi Muto!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.37,0:15:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll steal the top spot \Nfrom them with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the finished sample copy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is nice to be \Non the front cover.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda's manga is good.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.60,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like a straightforward shounen.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He drives by girls on \Npurpose to flip up their skirts.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Both his characters and \Nstory are typical mainstream.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's good too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mainstream...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna split the votes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.49,0:16:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda's on a roll.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.40,0:16:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Making a manga about your\N hobby sure has a big effect.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it comes down \Nto a new serialization
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and a one-shot, people are more likely to vote for the new serialization, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That trend does exist,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not a sure thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.25,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Buchigiri{\i0} has a clear goal of becoming the number one racer.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,430)}The race scenes are\N showy and intense.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0} has a lot of exposition
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and will look plain in comparison.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But the content is good, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.64,0:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, if they \Nunderstand what's going on.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The majority of the \Nreaders are in their teens.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.65,0:16:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Buchigiri{\i0} is easier for \Nthem to understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.78,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aida, what ranking do \Nyou think {\i1}PCP{\i0} will get?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it splits votes with {\i1}Buchigiri{\i0},
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,then it may be hard for it to get ahead of the other popular manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.46,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's all up to the readers.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the early results \Nare in tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told him to only let \Nus know the final results.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But I really want to know!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rankings, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Moriya, not again—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to know as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it does well.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.02,0:17:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It definitely will!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.82,0:17:35.99,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.99,0:17:38.74,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,{\i0\fad(0,450)}PCP{\i1} is the manga \Nthat must rank highly.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.66,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Will we place even with Niizuma?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.37,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}Or even higher?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.98,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what time will the\N final results be out?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from last time, the call could come as late as 5 PM.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, what time are \Nyour assistants coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,4:30.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he contacts us\N before they get here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's try calling him!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They may be out already!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.58,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll contact us as \Nsoon as they're out.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.26,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I read it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.01,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I thought it was really good!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.18,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I especially liked the part where they spent two weeks preparing
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.84,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,and in just one night,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.84,0:18:46.48,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,made a message with \Nflowers in the flower bed.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.39,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I wish someone would do that for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.44,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the assistants came already!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.94,0:18:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even 4 yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm astonished.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best by far.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,422 votes.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.21,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A 150 vote lead over 2nd place.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,1st place.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the door's open!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.30,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.68,0:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.64,0:19:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We got first place!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,By a landslide!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Saiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me in too!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.02,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}422 votes... we haven't seen that since {\i1}Crow{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Crow got 401.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And back then, there \Nwas no one-shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It got even more than {\i1}+Natural{\i0} did with its recent 1st place.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Natural{\i0} only got 310 votes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If there wasn't a one-shot, \Nhow would it have done?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd place with 268 votes?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.13,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Ashirogi was just \Ntoo overwhelming.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's frustrating.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a great vote tally.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda Shinta should make {\i1}Buchigiri{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the readers want.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.35,0:20:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can wrap up {\i1}Kiyoshi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a serialization \Nname for {\i1}Buchigiri{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, isn't that great?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I got beat pretty bad by Ashirogi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay them back\N with a serialization!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They did?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and by a landslide.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}+Natural{\i0} dropped to 8th place.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.04,0:20:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This was only because {\i1}PCP{\i0} \Nand {\i1}Buchigiri{\i0} were good...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rewrite it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.38,0:20:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.04,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot afford to lose\N to Takagi and Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.42,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rewrite everything you haven't sent to the printer yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.64,0:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So she said she wants to\N rewrite as much as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.77,0:20:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even what I'm drawing now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if possible...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.81,0:20:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina-sensei said she'll \Nmake it better, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.73,0:20:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.07,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If she wasn't that fired \Nup, I'd be disappointed!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.57,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't make it better,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi will overtake us!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Under 10 and over 18?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.75,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The main demographic voted too,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but those two age ranges\N were particularly conspicuous.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's analyze that and use\N it for reference going forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.80,0:21:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.55,0:21:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's set aside the \Ndifficult issues for now,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.92,0:21:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,since Hattori went out of \Nhis way to bring us a feast!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I realized it, \NI was at the grocery store...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have the results chart?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.22,0:21:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you're an author,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give it to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want it as a keepsake?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have someone \NI want to show it to.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I really can't give it to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.03,0:21:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Other authors' rankings are on here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.49,0:21:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no problem with
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.98,0:21:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you telling your own \Nrank to others, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you come with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.38,0:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for me to come too?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point if \Nwe aren't together.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.31,0:22:17.64,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.78,0:22:24.99,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.61,0:22:28.53,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This is what you wanted, \Nbut never managed to get.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.53,0:22:31.70,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,A first place ranking \Nin Weekly Shounen Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.74,0:23:18.20,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's not like I got \Nthis all by myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.25,0:23:21.67,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}Many people helped me.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.38,0:23:24.54,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,But Ashirogi Muto got 1st place!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.96,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,So what if your first \Nchapter got first place?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.67,0:23:32.01,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Of course it would.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.01,0:23:34.30,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Back when {\i1}Fist of the\N North Star{\i0} was popular,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.81,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,it got first place with\N more than 700 votes.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.32,0:23:38.89,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,The real challenge \Nstarts from here, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.15,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,When you get really popular
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.15,0:23:42.65,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,and are truly number one,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.02,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,come back here.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.15,0:23:50.32,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.08,0:23:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Six months.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.08,0:23:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see how it goes \Nuntil their 25th chapter.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.46,0:24:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If they get such low rankings
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.00,0:24:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that it should be canceled, then after their 7th chapter, I won't hesitate.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.75,0:24:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they aren't head to head
