Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.50,0:21:19.75,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I won't give up on it, won't be persuaded
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.75,0:21:26.05,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My dream is the one irreplaceable thing
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.05,0:21:31.26,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The chagrin I've felt I always bore with pride
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.26,0:21:37.81,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}This story will change all my solitude into something positive
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.81,0:21:44.40,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if we rise above our life, a different one awaits us
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.40,0:21:51.16,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,350)}I will cut a path for my future
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.41,0:21:59.50,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Inside my heart lies a dream I wish to protect
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.50,0:22:05.47,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}so I can go on believing, and chasing the wind
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.47,0:22:12.51,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}There is only one place I have my eyes set on: where we can laugh together
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.51,0:22:18.81,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}There lies a light that connects to the dream you gave me
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.81,0:22:24.61,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I will lead you towards a future neither of us is aware of yet
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.78,0:22:37.33,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,200)}When I look back I see my footsteps
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.00,0:22:43.13,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}made by countless moments of happiness and sorrow
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.13,0:22:49.80,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}This proof that I have lived until today is what lends me strength
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.80,0:22:56.52,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)}I will engrave it into my chest and walk forward with proud strides
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.52,0:23:05.57,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I have a dream I want to see through
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.57,0:23:11.66,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I can alight my passion, set fire to it
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.66,0:23:18.66,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}As we pursue our dreams, we will meet and split
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.66,0:23:24.92,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You taught me a strength only I wield
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.92,0:23:30.80,Insert-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I will stand up, go on, no matter how often I stumble
