Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.17,0:03:04.32,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fight won't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.33,0:03:10.58,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far I've come to achieve that?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.58,0:03:15.88,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In ten years time I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.88,0:03:22.39,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the scenario I wrote for myself, ensuring I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.39,0:03:29.02,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.02,0:03:35.36,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.07,0:03:44.07,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.07,0:03:50.33,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I fuel my passion until I succeed
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.33,0:03:57.09,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,There will be meetings and partings along the way
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.09,0:04:03.34,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.34,0:04:09.22,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,And rise back up again and again
